    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Routine exercises? That's a bit of a stretch given the timing and the sudden blackout of communications in those sectors. I've also had two different analysts mention specific logistics shipments that don't look like standard training gear. If you're certain it's just posturing, help me understand why those specific indicators are being flagged as anomalies if everything is as routine as you're saying?",
